snippet.title: Super Hamster Havoc - Steam Next Fest Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
Super Hamster Havoc is a top-down twin stick multiplayer arena shooter that’s all about frantic action and fun game play. Rush around colorful environments battling it out in quick rounds across various game modes. Fight with a wide array of weapons, explosives and kill streaks to dominate every game you play.

Play The Demo as a part of #steamnextfest : https://store.steampowered.com/app/1043780/Super_Hamster_Havoc/
Website: https://superhamsterhavoc.com
